Posted By: Bryan Long
I have decided to take offers on my t201 collection.  I would rather sell the group as a whole if possible, because I don't have much time to sell card by card.  If interested in the group, please send me an offer and maybe we can work something out.  I would also be willing to trade for HOFers and a trade/cash deal.  There are two cards that I just bought that have not arrived yet, but they should in a few days.
Thanks,
Bryan Long
